{"tid":401804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地覺得星座準唔準？","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T12:15:34.000Z","uid":138803,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"863683d6b16f7c2fd1d127805b9955b200cd685a","tid":401804,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"我以前覺得星座麻麻地準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我睇埋其他嗰啲月亮 上升 水象 星座 嗰啲<br />\n就幾準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fe14438747699b6bd0e3c2933fdec60e48329b","tid":401804,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:32:16.000Z","msg":"唔信，係d女仔先特別相信呢套"},{"pid":"4f504676a234c1ce7b3fffb670a69b776de948f1","tid":401804,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔信，係d女仔先特別相信呢套</blockquote><br />\n我見好多舊post<br />\n啲巴打都好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c7e45c528b546e2e6a0dc2f65cbd4900b05664","tid":401804,"uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"信啊 水瓶同雙子真係好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e500a72d081e1ecef8fcc191053f5c255202351","tid":401804,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲人話準 有啲人話唔準"},{"pid":"36bffeb20a79454f6baab1340ff1b51be9de26ed","tid":401804,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"準"},{"pid":"3badff8c142f1fcff54c72d37b5176579360a80a","tid":401804,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"信則有，不信則無。<br />\n<br />\n前前度個星座同我好夾，不論係佢or 其他女仔都咁講，但我同佢成日嘈交<br />\n<br />\n前度星座乜7 愛得好徹底，乜敢愛敢恨之類，當初佢都話&quot;雖然你唔知星座，但我呢個星座愛人會好徹底&quot;,  拍咁耐拖我罵都冇罵過佢，就因為一次佢唔知痴左乜線發脾氣就話要分手，我連自己衰d乜都唔知。個晚仲要係我生日！！！！！<br />\n(非帽事，佢仲單身緊)"},{"pid":"cba434b8ae75b13c7afb5d875675c07a08b09a19","tid":401804,"uid":41530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"對有睇開個啲人咪準囉，睇得多都會受影響"},{"pid":"c7f842d78e5ed3ac20bf5bd6ceaec26135eb0570","tid":401804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:17:09.000Z","msg":"星座講得好空泛"},{"pid":"6b1391a839a9a62fa44d91961141d0fdc9df9065","tid":401804,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信則有，不信則無。<br />\n<br />\n前前度個星座同我好夾，不論係佢or 其他女仔都咁講，但我同佢成日嘈交<br />\n<br />\n前度星座乜7 愛得好徹底，乜敢愛敢恨之類，當初佢都話&quot;雖然你唔知星座，但我呢個星座愛人會好徹底&quot;,  拍咁耐拖我罵都冇罵過佢，就因為一次佢唔知痴左乜線發脾氣就話要分手，我連自己衰d乜都唔知。個晚仲要係我生日！！！！！<br />\n(非帽事，佢仲單身緊)</blockquote><br />\n橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c49c6a6908bd1e69fe9f09488abf4a34f54d202","tid":401804,"uid":138803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對有睇開個啲人咪準囉，睇得多都會受影響</blockquote><br />\n睇我個星座成日話好就得人<br />\n我覺得自己唔係<br />\n睇極都唔準<br />\n反而其他準啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c617e558c73ce2fc903b62645b0c0d0b52c2b72","tid":401804,"uid":69484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"人既性格培養分先天後天，後天就係 家庭教育，成長經歷等等。但一對親兄弟都有唔同性格，呢個區別就係先天既影響<br />\n<br />\n咁先天就同所謂既星座有關，可能係因為懷孕時所受既太陽輻射，食物，環境，溫度等有關 <br />\n<br />\n與其話星座冇科學證明，不如你證明留以上既環境因素唔會對人有影響<br />\n<br />\n星座係一門統計學就比較貼切，大體上會準但都會受唔同因素影響"},{"pid":"3bf030839d0e8d2ad1afea888aad26e775aac8c5","tid":401804,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"星座唔係淨係睇邊日出世<br />\n重要睇埋幾點，甚麼年份等等 (詳情我都唔知)<br />\n但係依啲都係所謂 inheritant characters<br />\n性格既野，後天經歷會有更大影響<br />\n<br />\n但係好似啲戇㞗港女齋睇出世就好大機會唔準囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c6e9e75f639342831d1d4c84256e2b300101bb","tid":401804,"uid":31888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"點解邊年邊月邊日同幾點出世會影響性格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4c3b645657ce3927d56cbdc07afe4af6c76111","tid":401804,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"準"},{"pid":"690a914c8aefd1ecc33f5888dbe984e50f626c84","tid":401804,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:15:34.000Z","msg":"明明想覺得唔準但偏偏又講中晒D優點缺點嗰D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">當然你話個個都係咁咁我冇嘢好講</span></span>"}]}